

## HTTP2 via autoloading

This is a simple port of the PEAR HTTP2 library to make it use autoloading rather than require, and to be callable via static function, as the class has no state.


## Previous Readme

This package is http://pear.php.net/package/HTTP and has been migrated from http://svn.php.net/repository/pear/packages/HTTP

Please report all new issues via the PEAR bug tracker.

If this package is marked as unmaintained and you have fixes, please submit your pull requests and start discussion on the pear-qa mailing list.

To test, run either
$ phpunit tests/
  or
$ pear run-tests -r

To build, simply
$ pear package

To install from scratch
$ pear install package.xml

To upgrade
$ pear upgrade -f package.xml
